modName: The Ashen HD ESM File Fixed
summary: Re-formatted .esm file for The Ashen HD v2.5 for Seren4XX and RadioRagae.
descriptionHtml:
Re-formatted .esm file for The Ashen HD v2.5 for Seren4XX and RadioRagae.
This mod has been uploaded for the express purpose of transferring the file included to those users, and should not be downloaded by anyone excepting them. Please acquire the file from The Ashen mod, found here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/8583 when it is made available by the author.
author: DiabolusUrsus
